FBIS4-36332 "drnes110_a_94003" FBIS-NES-94-110 Daily Report 7 Jun 1994 ARAB AFRICA Algeria Newspaper Journalist Killed in Algiers Newspaper Journalist Killed in Algiers NC0706163294 Paris AFP in English 1453 GMT 7 Jun 94 NC0706163294 Paris AFP English BFN [Excerpt] Algiers, June 7 (AFP) -- Suspected Muslim extremists killed another Algerian journalist Tuesday [7 June] amid an escalation of attacks on civil servants, doctors and intellectuals as part of a fundamentalist campaign for power. The security services announced that Cherquit Ferhat of the government daily El Moudjahid was shot dead in central Algiers, but gave no further details immediately. [passage omitted]
